Prime Cabinet Secretary Musalia Mudavadi is scheduled to launch the Office of the Spouse to
the Prime Cabinet Secretary Tessie Shangatti Mudavadi on
Friday. In an invite seen by Citizen Digital, the
event will take place at the Movenpick Hotel, in Nairobi where her husband will be the
chief guest. “The Office of the Prime Cabinet Secretary H.E (DR) Musalia
Mudavadi, E.G.H. invites your Media House to the launch of the Office of the
Spouse to the Prime Cabinet Secretary.,” read a statement. “The Office of The Spouse to the Prime Cabinet Secretary was established by the Government to complement the work being done by the
Office of the First Lady and the Office of the Spouse to the Deputy President,”
he stated.